{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/airwallex\/paymentintentprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/airwallex\/paymentintentprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PaymentIntentProvider"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"PaymentIntentProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" enables delayed payment intent creation, allowing you to defer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the creation of a payment intent until just before payment confirmation or when it is required."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When using "},{"code":"Session","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with a payment intent provider instead of a pre-created intent,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the SDK will call "},{"code":"createPaymentIntent()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" asynchronously when needed. The provider"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"must also supply the basic payment information (amount, currency, customerId) synchronously."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Usage Example","level":2,"anchor":"Usage-Example"},{"code":["class MyPaymentIntentProvider: NSObject, PaymentIntentProvider {","    let amount: NSDecimalNumber = NSDecimalNumber(string: \"99.99\")","    let currency: String = \"USD\"","    let customerId: String? = \"customer_123\"","","    func createPaymentIntent() async throws -> AWXPaymentIntent {","        \/\/ Call your backend to create the payment intent","        let response = try await MyBackendAPI.createPaymentIntent(","            amount: amount.decimalValue,","            currency: currency,","            customerId: customerId","        )","        return response.paymentIntent","    }","}","","\/\/ Use with Session","let provider = MyPaymentIntentProvider()","let session = Session(","    paymentIntentProvider: provider,","    countryCode: \"US\",","    returnURL: \"myapp:\/\/payment\/return\"",")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Important-Notes","level":2,"text":"Important Notes","type":"heading"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"amount","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"currency","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"customerId","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" properties must return values immediately (they cannot be async)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The values returned by ","type":"text"},{"code":"amount","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"currency"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerId"},{"type":"text","text":" must match the values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AWXPaymentIntent"},{"type":"text","text":" returned by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"amount"},{"type":"text","text":" should be zero for recurring-only payments (no immediate charge)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"},{"type":"text","text":" method will only be called once, and the result is cached"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"},{"type":"text","text":" throws an error, the payment flow will fail"}]}]}]},{"type":"aside","name":"See Also","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"code":"Session","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"AWXPaymentIntent","type":"codeVoice"}]}],"style":"note"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@M@Airwallex@objc(pl)PaymentIntentProvider","modules":[{"name":"Airwallex"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"protocol","roleHeading":"Protocol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PaymentIntentProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PaymentIntentProvider"}],"title":"PaymentIntentProvider"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A protocol for providing payment intents on-demand during the payment flow.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex"]]},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider\/amount","doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider\/currency","doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider\/customerId"]},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Methods","title":"Instance Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider\/createPaymentIntent()"]}],"references":{"doc://org.cocoapods.Airwallex/documentation/Airwallex/PaymentIntentProvider/customerId":{"role":"symbol","title":"customerId","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The customer ID associated with this paym